.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, russian, nigerian, polish
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, indie, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the indian##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the nigerian is the fan of indie##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left of the russian##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the indian##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality      | nigerian     | indian       | russian | polish        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | folk       | soul     | dubstep    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

