5. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person who growsrose##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | analyst  | teacher    | social-worker | videographer |
