 2. the person eating banana is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the accountant is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person eating banana##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the writer##1
 6. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | banana  | pomegranate | orange     | blueberry |
| Job           | doctor  | writer      | accountant | dancer    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
