3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person drinking tea##1
9. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | tea           | juice    | lemonade    |
| Hobby         | traveling  | rock-climbing | drawing  | video-games |
